{"tid":1825442,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"「極恐怖」在酒店房間收到奇怪電話","createTime":"2020-01-15T09:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T08:04:27.000Z","uid":261290,"like":233,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"31d93d4f310c095b8966ff61722ac1a2df8c868b","tid":1825442,"uid":261290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"因為間屋漏水漏得好緊要，要出去租酒店住兩晚等維修，咁我同我妹租左間酒店一晚，check in左之後，我係16:30落一落街諗住買野食，我妹就係房睇電視等我。<br />\n係我落到地面時，我妹即時打比我，話我一離開房間不足30秒，房間個電話就響。<br />\n電話中有個男人好細聲好鬼祟咁問：要唔要打針？<br />\n我妹就問佢：你講咩話我聽唔清楚<br />\n個男人就變到用返正常聲音問：要唔要打針？<br />\n之後就收左線了<br />\n<br />\n我之後有去返酒店前台問職員，佢地都好驚訝，因為房間電話只可以內線打到，街外電話打唔到入黎。佢間酒店一層係得兩間房，職員幫我查左另一間房係無人。<br />\n<br />\n我地本身都估緊會唔會係另一間房有人打黎，但隔離房根本都無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗左好多個可能性但都解釋唔到，我真心好撚柒驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人有類似經歷，或者有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f20d647ee00a205d927b6172cb78bc24c13e37d","tid":1825442,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"Who Do You Call When the Police Murders？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1825419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1825419</a>"},{"pid":"bc42c758674ada8c8212143b4e66fc4d07df4b45","tid":1825442,"uid":68689,"like"